Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • project.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Consumer, Producer

    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
    A user can be of type producer or consumer The user can like documents that match the user's taste A list of users who a user follows or who follow a user is also maintained Users are given randomly generated IDs for identification This removes the need for user name input
    Author:
    Obinna Elobi
